CODE ATTRIBUTION
==============================================================================

Section A (Alex Zielenski):
  - Mousecape/Mousecape/src/models/         (ObjC model layer)
  - Mousecape/Mousecape/src/controllers/    (ObjC controllers)
  - Mousecape/mousecloak/                   (private API layer)

Section B (sdmj76):
  - Mousecape/Mousecape/SwiftUI/            (all SwiftUI interface code)
  - Mousecape/MousecapeHelper/              (Helper application)
  - Mousecape/mousecloak/main.swift         (CLI rewrite)
  - Mousecape/Mousecape/SwiftUI/Utilities/  (Windows cursor conversion,
    localization, debug logging)
  - README.md, CLAUDE.md, RELEASE_NOTES.md  (documentation)
  - .github/                                (CI/CD configuration)
